Bundled files:
  - vision_bundle.mjs                     (JS API)
  - vision_wasm_internal.{js,wasm}        (SIMD WASM runtime + glue)
  - vision_wasm_module_internal.{js,wasm} (module WASM runtime + glue)
  - vision_wasm_nosimd_internal.{js,wasm} (no-SIMD fallback runtime + glue)
  - gesture_recognizer.task               (trained hand gesture model)

No source modifications were made. To reproduce, install the package from npm
at the version pinned in the project's package.json and copy the corresponding
files from node_modules/@mediapipe/tasks-vision/.
